---
Diagnose tirith installation and configuration

Usage: tirith doctor [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>       Output format (default: human) [possible values: human, json]
      --reset-bash-safe-mode  Remove persistent bash safe-mode flag (re-enables enter mode)
      --fix                   Auto-fix detected issues
      --yes                   Auto-approve all fixes (no prompting)
  -h, --help                  Print help

Examples:
  tirith doctor
  tirith doctor --fix
  tirith doctor --fix --yes
